2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of neural networks and feature combination learning, which are common techniques in machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper's focus on NLP and machine learning techniques falls under the broader umbrella of AI research. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses the use of neural networks, which is a subfield of neural computing falling under the scope of cs.NE. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - Although not the primary focus of the paper, the use of feature embedding methods is also a common technique in computer vision, falling under the scope of cs.CV.
